  "description": "A long, modern bridge stretches across a calm body of water under a pale blue sky. The bridge is constructed with concrete pillars supporting a deck, and tall, white pylons rise from the water, connected by cables to support the structure. Several birds are flying above and parallel to the bridge, adding a sense of scale and movement to the scene. A hazy coastline with buildings and greenery is visible in the background. The water is relatively smooth, with gentle ripples.",
